headline: Wall Street Pours Billions Into Build-To-Rent Communities, Betting Big Against Home Ownership Amid High Prices and Interest Rates
summary: High home prices and stubbornly steep mortgage interest rates have put homeownership out of reach for many Americans. Wall Street has seized upon this, funding large swathes of luxury single-family suburban homes with everything an owner could want ...
